msgid "Menu - press 'OK'"
msgstr "Menu - tryk 'OK'"

msgctxt "#31402"
msgid "Enable startup video intro"
msgstr "Aktivér opstartsintrovideo"

msgctxt "#31405"
msgid "[B]MONITOR YOUR SYSTEM[/B][CR][CR]Check out your hardware · Monitor CPU usage[CR]Check Kodi revision number"
msgstr "[B]OVERVÅG DIT SYSTEM[/B][CR][CR]Se din hardware · Overvåg CPU-brug[CR]Tjek Kodi revisionsnummer"

msgctxt "#31406"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SYSTEM SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup and calibrate displays · Configure audio output · [CR]Set power saving options · Enable debugging"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURER SYSTEMINDSTILLINGER[/B][CR][CR]Konfigurer og kalibrer skærme · Konfigurer lydudgang ·[CR]Indstil strømsparingsindstillinger · Aktivér fejlfinding"

msgctxt "#31407"
msgid "[B]SETUP PROFILES[/B][CR][CR]Setup and manage user profiles · Enable login screen[CR]Change password · Add a profile picture"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURER PROFILER[/B][CR][CR]Konfigurer og administrer brugerprofiler · Aktivér loginskærm[CR]Skift adgangskode · Tilføj profilbillede"

msgctxt "#31409"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE TV SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Change full screen info · Manage EPG data settings"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURER TV-INDSTILLINGER[/B][CR][CR]Skift fuldskærmsinfo · Administrer indstillinger for EPG"

msgctxt "#31410"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SERVICE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup control of Kodi via UPnP and HTTP · Configure file sharing[CR]Enable Zeroconf · Configure AirPlay"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURER TJENESTER[/B][CR][CR]Opsæt styring af Kodi ved hjælp af UPnP og HTTP · Konfigurer fildeling[CR]Aktiver Zeroconf · Konfigurer AirPlay"

msgctxt "#31412"
msgid "Select section"
msgstr "Vælg sektion"

msgctxt "#31413"
msgid "Local subtitle available"
msgstr "Lokal undertekst tilgængelig"

msgctxt "#31414"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE PLAYER SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Configure video playback · Configure music playback · Configure picture slideshow[CR]Configure video language and subtitles"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURER AFSPILLERINDSTILLINGER[/B][CR][CR]Konfigurer videoafspilning · Konfigurer musikafspilning · Konfigurer billeddiasshow[CR]Konfigurer videosprog og undertekster"

msgctxt "#31415"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE MEDIA SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Set default select action · Configure file list options · Configure metadata options[CR]Manage databases"
msgstr "[B]KONFIGURER MEDIEINDSTILLINGER[/B][CR][CR]Indstil standard valghandling · Konfigurer filliste-indstillinger · Konfigurer metadata-indstillinger[CR]Administrer databaser"

msgctxt "#31421"
msgid "Select your Kodi user profile[CR]to login and continue"
msgstr "Vælg din Kodi brugerprofil[CR]for at logge ind og fortsætte"

msgctxt "#31427"
msgid "Skin Shortcuts is responsible for handling all aspects of the main menu."
msgstr "Skin Shortcuts er ansvarlig for at håndtere alle aspekter af hovedmenuen."

msgctxt "#31428"
msgid "The Grab Fanart script provides the random fanart slideshows for the main menu."
msgstr "Grab Fanart-scriptet leverer de tilfældige fanart-diasshows til hovedmenuen."

msgctxt "#31429"
msgid "Library Data Provider is a service that runs in the background to provide library data for widgets and live backgrounds as well as playlist statistics for infolines."
msgstr "Library Data Provider er en tjeneste, der kører i baggrunden for at levere biblioteksdata til widgets og live-baggrunde samt afspilningslistestatistik til infolinjer."

msgctxt "#31430"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white studio icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Ressourcebilledtilføjelse til visning af standardhvide studioikoner i skin."

msgctxt "#31431"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white recording label icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Ressourcebilledtilføjelse til visning af standardhvide pladeselskabsikoner i skin."

msgctxt "#31432"
msgid "Provides numerous Widget options and extended cast and crew metadata."
msgstr "Leverer talrige widget-muligheder og udvidede rollebesætnings- og crew-metadata."

msgctxt "#31433"
msgid "Skin Info Service is used to display movie set information throughout the skin."
msgstr "Skin Info Service bruges til at vise filmserieoplysninger i skin."

msgctxt "#31434"
msgid "Check MP3 Theme checks whether the user has put a theme.mp3 file in the corresponding movie/TV show folder to be played when browsing."
msgstr "Check MP3 Theme kontrollerer, om brugeren har placeret en theme.mp3-fil i den tilsvarende film/TV-serie-mappe, der skal afspilles ved gennemsyn."

msgctxt "#31450"
msgid "  •  Open Settings "
msgstr "  •  Åbn indstillinger "

msgctxt "#31451"
msgid "  •  Click to Install"
msgstr "  •  Klik for at installere"

msgctxt "#31473"
msgid "Aeon Tajo Helper provides the data to display the cast for movies and TV shows."
msgstr "Aeon Tajo Helper giver data til visning af rollebesætningen for film og TV-serier."

msgctxt "#31474"
msgid "CU LRC Lyrics is used to download, sync, and display lyrics during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "CU LRC Lyrics bruges til at downloade, synkronisere og vise tekster under musik i fuld skærm."

msgctxt "#31475"
msgid "Play Trailer makes possible to play movie trailers through a context menu. "
msgstr "Play Trailer gør det muligt at afspille filmtrailere via en kontekstmenu."

msgctxt "#31476"
msgid "Allows the use of Youtube to play trailers and other videos."
msgstr "Tillader brug af YouTube til at afspille trailere og andre videoer."

msgctxt "#31477"
msgid "Provides some cast actress images to be shown in video views."
msgstr "Leverer nogle rollebesætningsskuespillerindebilleder til visning i videovisninger."

msgctxt "#31478"
msgid "Artist Slideshow is used to display artist fanart for both the home screen and during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "Artist Slideshow bruges til at vise kunstnerfanart til både startskærmen og under musik i fuld skærm."

msgctxt "#31479"
msgid "AutoCompletion provides suggestions to be selected while using the virtual keyboard."
msgstr "AutoCompletion giver forslag til at vælge, mens du bruger det virtuelle tastatur."

msgctxt "#31480"
msgid "Library Editor Script uses JSON to directly edit your database information."
msgstr "Library Editor Script bruger JSON til direkte at redigere dine databaseoplysninger."

msgctxt "#31481"
msgid "Global Search makes possible to search among all the items (movies, TV shows, music, actors, etc.) in your collection."
msgstr "Global Search gør det muligt at søge blandt alle elementerne (film, TV-serier, musik, skuespillere osv.) i din samling."

